{"article_id":"Ca3BGmb0M0llRJ0D","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The Senate health care bill is dead again","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"after two conservative Republican senators said last night","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"they would not vote to advance the legislation","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"because it does not repeal enough of former President Barack Obama ' s signature health law .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"As GOP leaders scramble to find a new tactic","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that will allow them to strip health insurance from millions","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"while slashing taxes for the wealthy ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"President Donald Trump ' s media supporters have been left grasping for a message .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"The original bill ,","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"which Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell assembled through a secretive process","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and tried to rush through with little public debate ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"would lead to 22 million more Americans being uninsured at the end of the decade , largely due to cuts to Medicaid ;","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"many of those","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"who retain insurance under the bill","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"would pay more for fewer benefits .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"The bill was amended","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"after the Congressional Budget Office offered that verdict ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"but the GOP decided not to wait for a new score","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"before moving forward .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Democratic senators are universally opposed to the legislation ,","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"while the most moderate and conservative Republicans have also refused to sign on ,","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"either because it does too much or too little","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"to move away from Obamacare ' s improvements to the health care system .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Trump ' s propagandists look to him to set the tone for how to respond to bad news .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"But the message out of the White House has always been incoherent on health care ,","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"largely because the president seems to have no real interest in the various , serious policy debates","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"surrounding the future of health insurance for the American people","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"-- he just wants a win .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"In May , the president held a Rose Garden event","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"to celebrate the passage of the House bill ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"which he described as a \" great plan. \"","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Weeks later , he turned around","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"and privately called that legislation \" mean . \"","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"That sort of policy incoherence gets in the way","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"of formulating messaging around legislative setbacks .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Last night , for instance , Trump tweeted","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"that \" Republicans should just REPEAL failing ObamaCare now","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"& work on a new Healthcare Plan","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"that will start from a clean slate .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"Dems will join in ! \"","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"But that tactical messaging completely ignores the question","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"of what a good health care plan would look like ,","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"and whether the Senate bill","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that just went down in flames","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"met that criteria .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Without clearly defined heroes and villains or a clear policy vision ,","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"his media allies have been left to their own devices .","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"The noise machine is grinding to a halt .","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"Absent messaging from the top , here are a few ways","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"the pro-Trump media are responding :","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Most of Trump ' s propagandists are of the opinion","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"that Trump can not fail ;","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"he can only be failed .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"As such , they ' ve quickly turned their fire on McConnell and Speaker of the House Paul Ryan","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"( R-WI ) .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"\" I know","depth":17},{"id":56,"text":"the president is frustrated with the situation .","depth":17},{"id":57,"text":"A lot has been promised to him","depth":17},{"id":58,"text":"and not much delivered , \"","depth":17},{"id":59,"text":"Fox host Kimberly Guilfoyle said last night .","depth":15},{"id":60,"text":"\" I think","depth":17},{"id":61,"text":"this is a failure on the part of the leadership ,","depth":18},{"id":62,"text":"to be quite honest .","depth":18},{"id":63,"text":"Because they needed to get this to stick","depth":17},{"id":64,"text":"and to coalesce","depth":18},{"id":65,"text":"and get it done . \"","depth":18},{"id":66,"text":"\" Second failure for Mitch McConnell , \"","depth":17},{"id":67,"text":"Steve Doocy added on Fox & Friends this morning ,","depth":17},{"id":68,"text":"pointing to the bill ' s previous collapse last month .","depth":16},{"id":69,"text":"Knives out for McConnell on Trump 's favorite show Fox & Friends .","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"pic.twitter.com/NHcoO1Sf0d","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"- Matthew Gertz","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"( @ MattGertz )","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"July 18 , 2017","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"Not the @ DRUDGE_REPORT headline","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"you want to see","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"if u r GOP","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"who campaigned for 8 years on basically \" give us Washington","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"we will fix things \"","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"pic.twitter.com/JeF7bVzmoG","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"- Kendall Breitman","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"( @ KendallBreitman )","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"July 18 , 2017","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"If the Senate bill continues to struggle ,","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"and Trump doesn ' t publicly support McConnell ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"we could see calls for his replacement in the near future .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Trump ' s lack of interest in policy leaves his supporters plenty of room","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"to say","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that they didn ' t like the bill ,","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"without creating any dissonance about the fact","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"that the president supported the legislation .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Doocy went after the bill from the start this morning ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"saying ,","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"\" Ultimately , what undid this bill is","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"-- the one","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"that they are not going to vote on now --","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"is it was a lousy bill .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"I mean ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"it still had big taxes .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"It still had a lot of regulations .","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"It had that insurance company subsidy slush fund","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"that Rand Paul was talking about .","depth":14},{"id":102,"text":"It was not what the American people \" wanted .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"Notably ,","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"since Doocy also has little knowledge of or interest in policy ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"he can ' t really say what a good replacement would look like either ,","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"simply saying","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"Congress should \" get rid of all that stuff","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"and come up with something new . \"","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"One of the problems","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"Senate Republicans faced","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"in trying to push through health care legislation","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"is that","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"because they knew","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"no bill would attract enough Democratic support","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"to overcome a filibuster ,","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"they were trying to pass the bill with a 50-vote threshold through the budget reconciliation process .","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"But that process limits what can actually go into the bill ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"making full repeal of Obamacare extremely difficult .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"In order to sidestep that process ,","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"the hosts of Fox & Friends are calling for Senate Republicans to deploy the \" nuclear option \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"and eliminate the filibuster altogether ,","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"making all votes subject only to a majority vote .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"It ' s unclear how this would help pass a health care bill","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"since Republicans just demonstrated","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"they don ' t have 50 votes in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"but this morning Doocy , co-host Brian Kilmeade , and former White House press secretary Ari Fleischer all seemed eager to push through that proposal .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"A few hours later , Trump ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"who regularly watches Fox & Friends ,","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"chimed in ,","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"tweeting ,","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"\" The Senate must go to a 51 vote majority instead of current 60 votes .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Even parts of full Repeal need 60 .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"8 Dems control Senate .","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Crazy ! \"","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"F & F team calls for nuclear option to pass Obamacare and other Trump priorities with 50 votes .","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"Ari Fleisher is on board .","depth":9},{"i